Text: Revised Executive Meeting Aug am Cc NOTE The executive meeting originally scheduled for Thursday August from am will now take place from am cst in M Dining The toll free number has changed Toll free Intl Please be prepared to provide the operator with your name Thank you Jana Forwarded by Jana MillsHOUECT on PM Jana Mills PM To James M BannantineENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Sanjay BhatnagarENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Cliff CT Diomedes nron David HaugENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Rebecca McDonaldENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Kenneth NRON Jeffrey K nron cc Joseph W SuttonENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Pam BensonENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Rosalee NRON Tori L CT Katherine NRON Sherri NRON Marcia nron Stacy GuidrozENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Beena PradhanENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Susan CT Molly nron Rosane nron Alice HritzENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Loretta BrelsfordENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Elaine RodriguezENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Linda nron Subject Confidential Executive Meeting Aug am There will be an Executive Meeting to discuss the Business Plan and Strategy for Project Lightning on Thursday August from am in EB M If you are unable to attend in person you may use the following dial in numbers Toll free Intl You must provide the operator with your name if you are planning to dial in there is no numeric passcode Thank you Jana
